    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a major restoration project or a comprehensive source for parts. The engine currently has significant compression issues and requires a full overhaul, and the transmission is experiencing slipping in higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and frame, along with several dents and faded paint across the body. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional dashboard cluster. While it is mostly complete, it is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed from its location.",
