      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, it offers a visceral, analog driving experience. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics. While showing light patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally crisp, making it a prime candidate for a dedicated enthusiast.",
