    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scuff on the rear bumper reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster common for its age. All electronic features\u2014including the high-definition infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust and road-ready. It comes with a comprehensive service log, having recently undergone a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection. The tires offer approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide a firm, confident response. This is a reliable, attractive vehicle ready for its next chapter without the premium cost of a showroom-floor model.",
